tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name TEXT,
    interaction_date DATE,
    interaction_details TEXT,
    inquiry_type TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE interactions (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    interaction_datetime TIMESTAMP,
    customer_id INT,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE inquiries (
    inquiry_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    inquiry_datetime TIMESTAMP,
    customer_id INT,
    inquiry_topic VARCHAR(100),
    inquiry_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE interactions (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    interaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    type VARCHAR,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE inquiries (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    inquiry_date TIMESTAMP,
    category VARCHAR,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR,
    last_name VARCHAR,
    email VARCHAR,
    phone_number VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE interactions (
    interaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    interaction_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    interaction_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
  order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  product_id INT,
  order_date TIMESTAMP,
  quantity INT
);
